✅ Example Usage

Add Student

Enter id: 101
Enter name: Aman
Enter marks: 85
Student successfully added!!


View Students

Student{id='101', name='Aman', marks=85}


Update Student

Input student id to update: 101
Enter new Name: Aman Chahar
Enter new Marks: 90
Student Updated!!


Delete Student

Input student id to delete: 101
Student Deleted!!

